snippets.title: Provisioning listApiSpecs Sample
snippets.description: Returns matching specs.

snippets.title: Provisioning getApiSpec Sample
snippets.description: Returns a specified spec.

snippets.title: Provisioning getApiSpecContents Sample
snippets.description: Returns the contents of a specified spec. If specs are stored with GZip compression, the default behavior is to return the spec uncompressed (the mime_type response field indicates the exact format returned).

snippets.title: Provisioning createApiSpec Sample
snippets.description: Creates a specified spec.

snippets.title: Provisioning updateApiSpec Sample
snippets.description: Used to modify a specified spec.

snippets.title: Provisioning deleteApiSpec Sample
snippets.description: Removes a specified spec, all revisions, and all child resources (e.g., artifacts).

snippets.title: Provisioning tagApiSpecRevision Sample
snippets.description: Adds a tag to a specified revision of a spec.

snippets.title: Provisioning listApiSpecRevisions Sample
snippets.description: Lists all revisions of a spec. Revisions are returned in descending order of revision creation time.

snippets.title: Provisioning rollbackApiSpec Sample
snippets.description: Sets the current revision to a specified prior revision. Note that this creates a new revision with a new revision ID.

snippets.title: Provisioning deleteApiSpecRevision Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a revision of a spec.
